@DATABASE "Scramble Spirits"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Scramble Spirits"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                             Scramble Spirits
                             ================



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives Pl1" rxs "address command zxampoke(46114,0)"}      46114,0
@{"Infinite Lives Pl2" rxs "address command zxampoke(46212,0)"}      46212,0
@{"Lives Pl1 = x     " rxs "address command zxampoke(38266,255)"}      38266,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Lives Pl2 = x     " rxs "address command zxampoke(38385,255)"}      38385,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
